oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Medical ultrasound of the bovine abdomen
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Streeter, Robert N.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: ultrasound
abdomen
diagnostics
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Ultrasonography of the bovine abdomen can provide details about the form and function of many areas of the gastrointestinal and hepatobiliary systems otherwise undetectable without exploratory laparotomy. This discussion will review the application of ultrasonography to the diagnosis of disorders of the abdominal viscera in cattle.
